#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/signals.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Set the execution model (`BLOCKING`, `NON_BLOCKING`, or `VIRTUAL_THREAD`)."
msgstr "设置执行模式 `（BLOCKING` 、 `NON_BLOCKING` 或 `VIRTUAL_THREAD` ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/signals.adoc
msgid "The response type and callback; the callback receives a `SignalContext` and returns a `Uni`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/signals.adoc
